# Wo ist dein Stachel?

278
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:34,200
# Holle

279
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:37,920
# Holle, wo ist dein Sieg?

280
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:41,320
# Wo

281
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,480
# Wo

