385
00:34:07,520 --> 00:34:12,440
In this self-contained world,
the music-making that accompanied
every ritual and service

386
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:14,800
was traditional and conservative.

387
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:24,480
For the budding composer Bruckner,
this was a technical education

388
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:29,280
in Catholic church music at its
most refined, pure and profound.

