HARRY CHRISTOPHERS: We know
he loved the music of Palestrina
and other Renaissance composers.

391
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:44,960
Looked to the way that music
was built, and built on it.

392
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:49,800
Enlarged it into a whole
succession of masses

393
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,760
which tend to get bigger and bigger.

