00:35:59,760 --> 00:36:01,880
Hello. Hello.

397
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:04,040
Nice to meet you. It's a pleasure.

398
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:07,160
This is absolutely beautiful.

399
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:17,640
Friedrich,
you're one of the librarians in this
extraordinarily beautiful library.

400
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:20,480
I should put gloves on, shouldn't I?
Yes.

401
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,160
This book is...

402
