My reading of German is
non-existent. So that says...

405
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:36,440
"Missa Solemnis in B.

406
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:43,080
"Zur hochfeierlichen Infulierung
des hochwurdigsten Herrn Pralaten
Friedrich I."

407
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:48,880
The Provost was elected in 1854,

408
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:54,200
and for the feast, Anton Bruckner
composed this Missa Solemnis.

409
00:36:54,200 --> 00:36:56,880
So, this was printed in...

410
00:36:56,880 --> 00:37:00,320
It is handwritten by himself.

411
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,720
By Anton Bruckner.
So, this is by Bruckner?

412
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:04,240
Yes.

413
